data.description: Discover the best deal in the sought-after Botanica Lakes gated resort-style community w/ low HOA fees! This stunning home is offered furnished with 3 BRs, 2 baths, 2-car garage, & 1,690 sq ft of living space. Extremely well kept with nice open floorplan, split bedroom layout, & huge master suite with walk-in closet, soak tub, & 2 separate vanities. Impeccably designed kitchen w/ granite counters, dark wood cabinetry, & stainless appliances. Plenty of room to entertain in the formal dining room, eat in kitchen, & breakfast bar open to the living area. Tile flooring in the main living areas, and wood floors in the bedrooms. Enjoy the screened-in lanai for your morning coffee or evening relaxation. Whole home reverse osmosis and water filtration system. NEW Roof, Garage Doors, & Lanai Screens. Convenient location near the resort-style amenities of Botanica Lakes, an active community with heated lap pool & hot tub, fitness center, sauna, tennis & pickleball courts, clubhouse, and a calendar full of events. Centrally located, this home offers easy access to I-75, RSW International Airport, shopping, dining, and all the attractions of SWFL. Make Botanica Lakes your new home in paradise!
